Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中文字幕：dottob\N{\rEn}<b><i>Psagmeno.com</b> <font color=#ff0000>Subtitles / Screenshots / Trailers</font>
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派拉蒙影业\N{\rEn}Paramount
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维亚康姆公司\N{\rEn}A VIACOM COMPANY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工厂[葡语]电影[西语]\N{\rEn}FÁBRICA DE CINE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,通路实业电影\N{\rEn}<font color=#ff0000>A</font>ccess <font color=#ff0000>I</font>ndustries FILM
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}译者注\N1549年，天主教传教士\N圣·弗朗西斯·泽维尔\N(Saint Francis Xavier)\N在日本鹿儿岛开始传教\N\N1613年，德川家康发布禁教令，幕府在全国禁止天主教\N长崎云仙山区成为屠杀长崎地区天主教徒的场所\N岛原天主教徒劫难始于此时\N\N{\rTop_cn}引自：http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_3f8e0f520101iauv.html
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}译者注\N1627年，松仓重政首创了“云仙地狱”的拷问方式\N将教徒倒悬温泉正上方，受高温硫磺毒气熏蒸\N在其气绝之前拖上缓和呼吸后，再吊回原位继续折磨\N\N{\rTop_cn}引自：http://www.sanada.net.cn/shiliao/shiliao_38.htm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}译者注\N1629年，水野守信首先于长崎实践以“踏绘”形式识别天主教徒的做法\N所谓“踏绘”，即把圣像置于受检人面前，强迫践踏\N\N{\rTop_cn}引自：http://www.sanada.net.cn/shiliao/shiliao_38.htm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}译者注\N“穴吊”：将囚犯捆绑倒吊，头部插入大小如缸深坑\N耳后开口让血缓慢渗出，再用似枷木具从脖子两侧封住坑口\N埋住头部，持续多日致死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10}译者注\N1634年，日本爆发反横征暴敛，反宗教迫害的农民大起义，即\N“岛原(、天草)之乱”\N\N{\rTop_cn}引自：http://www.qulishi.com/huati/daoyuanzl/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默\N{\rEn}Silence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赞美您，我主耶稣基督\N{\rEn}Praise to you, Lord Jesus Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.00,0:02:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始\N{\rEn}始め
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1633，主的平安[拉丁语]，赞美神\N{\rEn}1633. Pax Christi. Praised be God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然于我们，如今此地再无和平\N{\rEn}Although for us. There is little peace in this land now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从未了解日本，当它成为文明之都\N{\rEn}I never knew Japan, when it was a country of light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我没想到它会如当前这般黑暗\N{\rEn}But I have never known it to be as dark as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们所有进展都被新的迫害终止...\N{\rEn}All our progress has ended in new persecution...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新的镇压，新的苦难\N{\rEn}New repression, new suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们使用有洞的杓子(长柄勺)\N{\rEn}They use ladles filled with holes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让水慢慢漏出\N{\rEn}So the drops would come out slowly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使痛苦持续更久\N{\rEn}And the pain would be prolonged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.78,0:03:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每滴溅落的水花\N{\rEn}Each small splash of the water,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有如滚碳\N{\rEn}Was like a burning coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长崎奉行官抓了四名修士(奉行：大小藩的地方官)\N{\rEn}The Governor of Nagasaki took four friars,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我们在云仙的一个自属教会\N{\rEn}and one of our own society to Unzen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里有温泉\N{\rEn}There are hotsprings there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.69,0:03:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本人称之为：“云仙地狱”\N{\rEn}The Japanese call them: Hells
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.78,0:03:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一方面，我以为，讲笑\N{\rEn}Partly, I think, in mockery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.97,0:03:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又一方面，我必须告诉你，讲真\N{\rEn}and partly, I must tell you, in truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,官员们要我们的教士抛弃神及神的爱的福音\N{\rEn}The officials told our Padres to abandon God and the gospel of his love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.78,0:03:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而他们不只是拒绝弃教\N{\rEn}But they not only refused to apostatize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们要求受折磨\N{\rEn}They asked to be tortured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样，他们就可以证明他们信仰的力量\N{\rEn}So they could demonstrate the strength of their faith
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而神将与他们同在\N{\rEn}and the presence of God within them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些留在山上，长达33天\N{\rEn}Some remained on the mountain, for 33 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.16,0:04:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的勇气故事把希望给了我们的传教士\N{\rEn}The story of their courage gives hope to those of us priests
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.72,0:04:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些潜藏此处者\N{\rEn}who remain here in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会抛弃我们潜藏的基督徒\N{\rEn}We will not abandon our hidden Christians.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.52,0:04:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些身陷恐惧者\N{\rEn}Who live in fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只会变得更强，籍由主爱\N{\rEn}We only grow stronger in his love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,费雷拉和我们失联\N{\rEn}Ferreira is lost to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他最后一封信\N{\rEn}This was his last letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何失联？\N{\rEn}Why lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此信送交我处，正值你旅行葡萄牙之际\N{\rEn}This letter came to us, when you were traveling from Portugal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它经年始至我处，被藏匿、走私、赎回\N{\rEn}It took years to reach us, it was hidden, smuggled, ransomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.98,0:05:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最终交至我手则由一位荷兰商贩\N{\rEn}And finally put into my hand by a Dutch trader,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位同携其它消息者\N{\rEn}Who had other news as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他活着吗\N{\rEn}He is alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传闻他已弃教\N{\rEn}That he apostatized.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说他公开谴责神，抛弃了其信仰\N{\rEn}That he denounced God in public and abandoned his faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今已成为一名日本人\N{\rEn}And is now living as a Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.25,0:05:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能\N{\rEn}That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父费雷拉冒死于日本各地传播我等信仰\N{\rEn}Father Ferreira risked his life to spread our faith all over Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有今天都因为他\N{\rEn}We're here today because of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，他曾是...他是我们中最强大的\N{\rEn}Yes, he was... he is the strongest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.36,0:05:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他写下那些话，正值所有迫害最为彻底\N{\rEn}He wrote those words during the most sweeping persecution of all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在情况则更糟\N{\rEn}Now things are even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数千人死去\N{\rEn}Thousands are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们带给他们那些\N{\rEn}Because of what we brought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有数千人已放弃他们的信仰\N{\rEn}Thousands more have given up their faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说这商贩带来消息，只是未经证实，是吗\N{\rEn}You said this trader brought news, but it's not proven, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它可能是个诽谤以深入瓦解我等信仰\N{\rEn}It could be a slander created to further discredit our faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考虑到该国的迫害程度\N{\rEn}Given the extent of the persecution in that country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恕我失敬，那里定有大众仍需我们\N{\rEn}Respectfully, there must multitudes there who need us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.82,0:06:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而事实上，信中他再无多言\N{\rEn}And the fact, there has been no other word of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 至于那些消息经由荷兰...- 谣言，神父，只是\N{\rEn}- And the news brought by the Dutch... - Rumors, Father, only.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须推断，那是真的\N{\rEn}I must conclude, it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-如果是真的，神父\N{\rEn}-If it is true, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.25,0:06:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那它意味着啥\N{\rEn}What would it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对耶稣会，对于整个欧洲的天主教\N{\rEn}For the Jesuits. For the whole of Catholic Europe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来，我们此番使命，紧迫尤胜以往\N{\rEn}It's seems to me that our mission here, is more urgent than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得去找到神父费雷拉\N{\rEn}We must go find Father Ferreira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不允许那样\N{\rEn}I can not allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.87,0:06:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎，我们怎能放弃我们的使命\N{\rEn}How. How can we abandon our mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.66,0:06:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的使命，神父加佩\N{\rEn}Your mission, Father Garupe,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是找到费雷拉的消息，你已找到了\N{\rEn}was to find word of Ferreira, you have found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-原谅我神父，只是这封信\N{\rEn}-Excuse me Father, but this letter
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲述了最可怕的故事\N{\rEn}Relates the most terrible story,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,却只字未提费雷拉本人\N{\rEn}but it says nothing of Ferreira himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他出了啥事仍是未知\N{\rEn}Whatever happened to him is still unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们所知其命运的全部，只是这诽谤\N{\rEn}All that we know of his fate, is this one slander.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请允许我，神父范礼安，但\N{\rEn}Permit me, Father Valignano, but
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.73,0:07:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信我们的使命依然成立\N{\rEn}I believe our mission still stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可知有多少基督徒？在岛原半岛被当局处决\N{\rEn}Do you know how many Christians, the authorities executed in Shimabara?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数千人，数以万计\N{\rEn}Thousands, tens of thousands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们大多数被斩首\N{\rEn}Most of them beheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.32,0:07:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，对你们来说太危险了\N{\rEn}No, it's far too dangerous for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，但神父\N{\rEn}Yes, but Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.60,0:07:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们怎能忽视那个以信仰养育我们的人\N{\rEn}how can we neglect the man who nurtured us in faith?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他为我们塑造了世界\N{\rEn}He shapes the world for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使诽谤是真的\N{\rEn}And even if the slander should be true
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.27,0:07:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而神父费雷拉有罪。-是的\N{\rEn}then Father Ferreira is damned. - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们别无选择除了拯救他的灵魂\N{\rEn}We have no choice but to save his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:07:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是你们俩真心所想？-是的\N{\rEn}- This is in your hearts in both of you? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\rEn}It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有如我们当初的热诚\N{\rEn}Like our first fervor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我必须相信是神安排它在那儿\N{\rEn}Then I must trust God has put it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.58,0:08:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他招唤你们来场伟大的考验\N{\rEn}He calls you to a great trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一旦你们涉足该国\N{\rEn}The moment you set foot in that country,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们步入险境\N{\rEn}you step into high danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们将是派往的最后两位传教士\N{\rEn}You will be the last two priests to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人的军队\N{\rEn}An army of two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3月25日，1640。主的平安，神的荣誉\N{\rEn}May 25th, 1640. Pax Christi, God be praised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父范礼安，当我写下这些字句\N{\rEn}Father Valignano, as I begin these lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不肯定它一旦完成，它还能抵达你处\N{\rEn}I can not be sure that once they are done, they will ever reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想保持您对我们使命的信心\N{\rEn}But I want to maintain your confidence in our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,及证明您对我们的信任\N{\rEn}And vindicate your faith in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天，有个极好的消息\N{\rEn}Today, there was wonderful news.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您的常先生找到艘中国船\N{\rEn}Your Mr.Chiong has found us a Chinese boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.19,0:08:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它将偷运我们去日本\N{\rEn}It will smuggle us into Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.36,0:09:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还说他在澳门找到了唯一的日本人\N{\rEn}And he claims he's found the only Japanese in Macau.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可当我们在该国的最佳向导\N{\rEn}To be our most valued guide in that country.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，这边\N{\rEn}Come on，this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.66,0:09:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后，我们见到了首位日本人\N{\rEn}Finally, we meet our first Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不贵，你会明白\N{\rEn}He is not much, you will see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.82,0:09:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但差不多两月了，他是唯一的一个\N{\rEn}But after almost two months, he is the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.71,0:09:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒\N{\rEn}Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，起来\N{\rEn}Come on, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在海上漂流，葡萄牙人救了他\N{\rEn}He was drifting on sea. Portuguese bring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:10:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被困此处，想要回家\N{\rEn}He's stuck here. Wants to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他？你真是日本人\N{\rEn}Is he? Are you really Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会带你回家\N{\rEn}They will take you home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你家在哪儿\N{\rEn}Where is your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长崎\N{\rEn}Nagasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.45,0:10:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干哪行\N{\rEn}What's your work?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫他干啥都行\N{\rEn}He will do what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂我们的话\N{\rEn}You know our language?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂点\N{\rEn}Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，懂点\N{\rEn}Yes. Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.07,0:10:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从耶稣会教士学的\N{\rEn}You learned from the Jesuit Padres,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定曾，因此\N{\rEn}you must have, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.92,0:10:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是基督徒\N{\rEn}You're Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\rEn}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是基督徒\N{\rEn}No Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好向导归你，他也是基督徒\N{\rEn}Good guide for you, he's Christian too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:10:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是基督徒\N{\rEn}I am not Christian!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.20,0:11:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基督徒死了\N{\rEn}Christians die!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.66,0:11:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们死在长崎了\N{\rEn}They die in Nagasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-听我说\N{\rEn}-Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.53,0:11:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有钱\N{\rEn}We have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如你肯帮我们，我们就带你回家\N{\rEn}If you can help us, we can take you home
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就带你回日本的家\N{\rEn}We can take you home to Japan,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想回日本的家吗\N{\rEn}would you like to go home to Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想\N{\rEn}I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想回家\N{\rEn}I want to go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要钱\N{\rEn}No for money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.17,0:11:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本是我的祖国\N{\rEn}Japan is the country of my family!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我求你，别抛弃我，神父\N{\rEn}I beg you, don't abandon me here, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托\N{\rEn}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带我回家\N{\rEn}Take me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.03,0:11:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会是个好向导\N{\rEn}He will be good guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答应我。-我给你洗洗！他们带我回家\N{\rEn}Promise me. -I'll clean you up! They take me home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答应我\N{\rEn}Promise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的向导\N{\rEn}Our guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是基督徒\N{\rEn}He can't be Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他不是，但你能信他所说的一切？\N{\rEn}He says he's not, but can you believe anything he says?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至不愿相信他是日本人\N{\rEn}I don't even want to believe he is Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.50,0:12:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他又对他们说：你们要到全世界去，\N{\rEn}And he said to them: Go ye into the whole world，\N{\rTop_cn}(注：《兰斯杜埃版圣经》马可福音 第16章第15节[Douay-Rheims Bible 16:15])
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.85,0:12:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...将福音传给众生。\N{\rEn}...and preach the gospel to every (living) creature.\N{\rTop_cn}(注：该版本无括号内单词)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至有如此人\N{\rEn}Even to one such as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们的主吩咐过\N{\rEn}So our Lord commanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而当我准备如他所托，我看到他的脸在我面前\N{\rEn}And as I prepare to do his work, I see his face before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他看起来像当他必须吩咐彼得时\N{\rEn}He looks as he must have when he commanded Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.59,0:12:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂养我的羊羔\N{\rEn}"Feed My lambs."\N{\rTop_cn}(注：约翰福音 21:15)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂养我的羊羔，喂养我的羊\N{\rEn}"Feed my lambs.""Feed my sheep."\N{\rTop_cn}(注：约翰福音 21:15,17)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这震撼了我\N{\rEn}It fascinates me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感受到对他伟大的爱\N{\rEn}I feel such great love for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加佩和我当然没行李带往日本\N{\rEn}Garrpe and I had absolutely no luggage to bring to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.24,0:13:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我们自己的心\N{\rEn}Except our own hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在航行的平静和风暴中\N{\rEn}And during the calm and storm of the voyage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回想过去的20年\N{\rEn}I reflected upon the 20 years which has passed
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从迫害爆发以来\N{\rEn}since the persecution has broken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本的黑土地充满了那么多哀号的基督徒\N{\rEn}The black soil of Japan is filled with the wailing of so many Christians.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传教士的赤血已流淌太多\N{\rEn}The red blood of priests has float profusely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教堂的墙已被推倒\N{\rEn}The walls of churches have fallen down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已将生命托付此人\N{\rEn}We have committed our lives to this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.18,0:14:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-主所托付者更多\N{\rEn}-Jesus entrusted more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧\N{\rEn}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿，这儿\N{\rEn}Here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 吉次郎! 你去哪儿\N{\rEn}- Kichijiro! Where you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉次郎\N{\rEn}Kichijiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要背叛我们\N{\rEn}He is going to betray us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉次郎\N{\rEn}Kichijiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(用拉丁语祷告)\N{\rEn}(Praying in Latin)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(用拉丁语祷告)\N{\rEn}(Praying in Latin)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.03,0:14:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你祷告得太快了\N{\rEn}What you will do too quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父(葡萄牙语)\N{\rEn}Padre?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.02,0:16:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点，我们没时间了，没时间\N{\rEn}Hurry, we have no time. No time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方是哪儿\N{\rEn}What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友義村\N{\rEn}Tomogi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日本\N{\rEn}Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请快点\N{\rEn}Please be quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样危险看不到你\N{\rEn}So dangers can not see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉，神父\N{\rEn}I'm sorry, Padre.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了，处决尤甚以往\N{\rEn}Too dangerous, there are more executions than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.19,0:16:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们知道我们是基督徒\N{\rEn}If they know we are Christians.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会被杀掉\N{\rEn}We will be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝听到你了\N{\rEn}The Lord hears you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，他把你们派给我们\N{\rEn}Yes. He sent you to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请，进来，进来\N{\rEn}Please. Enter, enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.43,0:17:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rEn}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.21,0:17:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有点吃的，如果你们愿意\N{\rEn}We have little food. If you would like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们会安处此地直至早上\N{\rEn}You will be safe here till morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧，坐吧，请\N{\rEn}Sit, sit, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.02,0:17:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉，对不起\N{\rEn}I'm sorry. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这样怎么活\N{\rEn}How do you live like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我指，你们作为基督徒怎么活\N{\rEn}I mean, how do you live as Christians.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当危险如此之巨\N{\rEn}When the danger is so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你懂吗\N{\rEn}You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们秘密祈祷，但我们有爷爷大人(じいさま)\N{\rEn}We pray in secret, but we have a Jiisama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷大人\N{\rEn}Jiisama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁是爷爷大人\N{\rEn}Who is the Jiisama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你领导他们？你领导村庄\N{\rEn}You lead them? You lead the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.34,0:18:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祷告？祈祷\N{\rEn}In prayer, in devotions?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.73,0:18:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他能施行的唯一圣礼是洗礼\N{\rEn}The only sacrament he can perform is baptism.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.39,0:18:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们跟爷爷大人做礼拜，我们隐藏基督像\N{\rEn}We worship with the Jiisama, we hide the Christian images.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神依旧眷顾我们？\N{\rEn}God still sees us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是吗？是的\N{\rEn}- Yes? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我们没有传教士，直到现在\N{\rEn}Even though we don't have a priest, until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请吃\N{\rEn}Please eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请吃\N{\rEn}Please eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\rEn}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此每位基督徒都是我们秘密教会一份子\N{\rEn}Every Christian here is part of our secret church.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种信仰，这种信仰，你们有此信仰，如此强大\N{\rEn}This faith, this faith, this faith you have, is so strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.15,0:19:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们能有这般勇气\N{\rEn}You have such courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.80,0:19:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是这儿有此信仰，还是\N{\rEn}It is only here that there is such faith or...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其它村庄也有\N{\rEn}...in other villages too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道别的村\N{\rEn}We do not know about other villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们从不去那儿\N{\rEn}We never go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不去\N{\rEn}You don't go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.23,0:19:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别的村太危险了\N{\rEn}Other villages are so dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知该信任谁\N{\rEn}You do not know who to trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都害怕奉行官\N{\rEn}Everyone fears the Inquisitor,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,井上大人\N{\rEn}Inoue Sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.82,0:20:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,供出基督徒\N{\rEn}Inform on Christian,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们给你壹佰枚银币\N{\rEn}and they give you 100 pieces of silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贰佰拿基督修道士\N{\rEn}200 for a Christian brother
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.27,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿传教士，叁佰\N{\rEn}and for priest. 300.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叁佰\N{\rEn}300.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须去别的村\N{\rEn}We must go to the other villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须让他们知道传教士又来这儿了\N{\rEn}You must let them know that priests are here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们又来日本这儿了\N{\rEn}And we are here in Japan again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会好起来的\N{\rEn}It would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.26,0:20:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传闻\N{\rEn}There was hears
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.26,0:20:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有位神父，曾在此处\N{\rEn}a Padre, who was here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫做费雷拉\N{\rEn}called Ferreira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父费雷拉\N{\rEn}Father Ferreira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.49,0:20:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听说过他吗\N{\rEn}Have you heard of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,象我们\N{\rEn}Like us？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.29,0:20:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没。- 没\N{\rEn}No. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们不吃吗\N{\rEn}You do not eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.88,0:21:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是为{\rTop_cn}(感谢){\rDefault}你们{\rTop_cn}(教导我们信仰主){\rDefault}准备的\N{\rEn}It is you who feed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.74,0:22:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不敢经由大路带我们去别处\N{\rEn}They do not dare take us anywhere by the main road.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如此潜行真是个可怕的负担\N{\rEn}To hide like this must be a terrible burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.55,0:22:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被来自这些人的珍视的感受淹没\N{\rEn}I was overwhelmed by the love I felt from these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.67,0:22:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使他们脸上并无明示\N{\rEn}Even though their faces couldn't show it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.35,0:22:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多年的保密，已使他们的脸成为面具\N{\rEn}Long years of secrecy, have made their faces into masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.49,0:22:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何他们非得痛苦如斯\N{\rEn}Why do they have to suffer so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.97,0:22:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何神让他们忍受这般负累\N{\rEn}Why did God make them to bear such a burden?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.36,0:22:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是这儿最安全的\N{\rEn}This is the safest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.11,0:22:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是做木炭的小屋\N{\rEn}This hut for making charcoal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 当你听到这种声音\N{\rEn}- When you hear this sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.43,0:23:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们\N{\rEn}It will be us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你听到任何不一样\N{\rEn}If you hear anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.07,0:23:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏住\N{\rEn}Hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.10,0:23:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白天我们紧闭小屋门扉\N{\rEn}During the day we keep the door of our hut tightly closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.22,0:23:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,力求悄无声息\N{\rEn}And refrain from the slightest noise,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.30,0:23:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以免外面路过的人听到\N{\rEn}lest anyone passing outside may hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.54,0:23:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有天黑才可安全的下山进村\N{\rEn}Only the dark makes it safe for us to go down into the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去主持信徒\N{\rEn}And administer to the faithful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于，他们有了传教士可以原谅他们的罪\N{\rEn}Finally, they had priests to forgive their sins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.55,0:23:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赐福我，神父，我有罪啊\N{\rEn}Bless me Padre, for I have sinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:23:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忏悔。- 我有罪\N{\rEn}Confession. - I have sinned!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.13,0:24:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次？\N{\rEn}One more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.30,0:24:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？从头开始吗\N{\rEn}What? From the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.18,0:24:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来一次\N{\rEn}One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.17,0:24:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们整夜聆听他们的忏悔\N{\rEn}We heard their confessions all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.87,0:24:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我们并非总能确定告解的是什么\N{\rEn}Even though we could not always be sure what was being confessed
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.46,0:24:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在天主教带来了爱\N{\rEn}And now Christianity brought love，
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.79,0:24:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尊严，既第一次被视为神的子民而非牲畜\N{\rEn}The dignity for the first time of being treated like God's creatures, not animals
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.59,0:24:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及承诺，既他们所有的苦难不会以虚无终结\N{\rEn}And the promise that all their suffering would not end in nothingness，
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.73,0:24:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是救赎\N{\rEn}But in salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.17,0:24:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在深夜举行弥撒\N{\rEn}We offer mass in the dead of night.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.92,0:24:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像他们在地下墓穴做那样\N{\rEn}Just as they did in the catacombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.95,0:24:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻声地\N{\rEn}Quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.37,0:25:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在与神同在天堂了？\N{\rEn}We now are with God in Paradiso?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.74,0:25:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 天堂？天堂！- 是的，天堂\N{\rEn}- Paradiso? Paradise? - Yes, paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.56,0:25:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在？- 是的\N{\rEn}Now? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.20,0:25:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是\N{\rEn}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.42,0:25:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在神就在那儿\N{\rEn}But God is there now
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.00,0:25:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 直至永远\N{\rEn}- and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.95,0:26:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他为我们大家准备了位置，即使现在\N{\rEn}He prepares a place for us all, even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.51,0:26:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，塞巴斯蒂，为我的不耐烦\N{\rEn}Sorry Sebastian for my impatience.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.47,0:26:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为我的挫折甚感羞愧\N{\rEn}I'm ashamed of my frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.47,0:26:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子现已安享神的恩典，那才是重要的\N{\rEn}The child is safe in the grace of God now, and that is what is important.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.31,0:26:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你是个不良耶稣会士\N{\rEn}And you're a bad Jesuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.55,0:26:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我厌倦了整日被困此处\N{\rEn}I'm sick of being trapped in here all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.69,0:26:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧\N{\rEn}Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.59,0:26:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们甚至不知神父费雷拉是生是死\N{\rEn}We don't even know if Father Ferreira is alive or dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.00,0:26:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村民们从未听说过他\N{\rEn}The villagers never even heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.70,0:26:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人太担惊受怕了\N{\rEn}These people are so frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.69,0:27:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,满脑子恐惧，还有虱子\N{\rEn}There's fear over their heads and lice.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.88,0:27:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们有我们，我们使他们安心\N{\rEn}They have us, we comfort them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.80,0:27:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们还需坚持到几时\N{\rEn}How much longer can we do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.93,0:27:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们请缨这使命，弗朗西斯科\N{\rEn}We asked for this mission, Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.34,0:27:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们祈求此番历练，然后神听到了\N{\rEn}We prayed for this in the exercises. God heard us then.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.00,0:27:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在他也听着我们\N{\rEn}And he hears us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.84,0:27:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也许他能引导我们找到费雷拉，如此我们就能知道真相\N{\rEn}Then may he guide us to Ferreira, so we can know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.06,0:27:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得那可能吗？他的力量失去了\N{\rEn}You think it's possible that his strength gave up
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.66,0:27:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴在筑后守面前，像狗一样献上膝盖\N{\rEn}And he groveled to this Inquisitor anyway, went on his knees like a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.48,0:27:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谣言就是那样\N{\rEn}That so is the rumor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.09,0:27:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使井上是公认的魔鬼，费雷拉必能对抗他\N{\rEn}Even if Inoue is the devil everyone claims, Ferreira would stand up to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.21,0:27:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们俩有一个得去长崎找到他\N{\rEn}One of us must go to Nagasaki and find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.78,0:27:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那太危险\N{\rEn}It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.55,0:27:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们，对那些庇护我们的人\N{\rEn}For us, for the people who shelter us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.38,0:27:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们派吉次郎去，他带回消息我们再行动\N{\rEn}We sent Kichijiro and he brings back word we can act on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.11,0:27:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你疯了吗\N{\rEn}Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.20,0:28:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪儿\N{\rEn}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.85,0:28:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他并不在此\N{\rEn}He's never here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.71,0:28:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他总是喝醉，你知他不可信\N{\rEn}He's always drunk, you know he can't be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.52,0:28:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那咋整啊？我们总得做点啥好找到神父费雷拉\N{\rEn}What do we do? We must do something to find Father Ferreira!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.50,0:28:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们出去，我们冒个险，只呆一会儿\N{\rEn}Let's go out. Let's risk it. Just for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.82,0:28:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看啦\N{\rEn}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.32,0:28:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是神的信号\N{\rEn}That's God's sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.37,0:29:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别动\N{\rEn}Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.56,0:29:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在盯着我们\N{\rEn}Someone's here watching us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.01,0:29:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父\N{\rEn}Padre.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.72,0:29:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父\N{\rEn}Padre.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.51,0:30:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是暗号\N{\rEn}That is not the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.35,0:30:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 神父\N{\rEn}- Padre.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.00,0:30:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别害怕，没事的\N{\rEn}- Do not be afraid. It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.00,0:30:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们不会伤害你们\N{\rEn}- We won't hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.50,0:30:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们是基督徒，神父\N{\rEn}- We're Christians, Padre.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.50,0:30:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 基督徒！\N{\rEn}- Christian!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.50,0:30:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 基督徒！\N{\rEn}- Christian!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.78,0:30:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们需要你们\N{\rEn}- We need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.25,0:30:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别，别\N{\rEn}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.37,0:30:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塞巴斯蒂安！别！塞巴斯蒂安\N{\rEn}Sebastian! No! Sebastian!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.31,0:30:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父\N{\rEn}Padre!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.83,0:31:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们吓着你们，我们很抱歉\N{\rEn}We frightened you, we are sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.06,0:31:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们想请求你们去我们村，去五岛\N{\rEn}We want to ask you to come to our village. To Goto.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.81,0:31:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那儿的人失去其信仰，我们的孩子需要你们\N{\rEn}People miss our faith there. Our children need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.53,0:31:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们没弥撒，没忏悔\N{\rEn}We have no mass, no confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.72,0:31:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能做的只有祷告\N{\rEn}All we can do is pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.62,0:31:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎知我们在这儿\N{\rEn}How did you know we were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.01,0:31:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁告诉你的\N{\rEn}Who told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.79,0:31:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个信徒吗\N{\rEn}Did one of the faithful?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.66,0:31:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们村的基督徒，吉次郎\N{\rEn}It was a Christian of our village, Kichijiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.33,0:31:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉次郎\N{\rEn}Kichijiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.87,0:31:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们，我们，我们的吉次郎\N{\rEn}Our, our, our Kichijiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.36,0:31:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他跟你们一起来这儿\N{\rEn}He said he came here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.44,0:32:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，但他不是基督徒\N{\rEn}Yes, but he's not a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.75,0:32:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，他是\N{\rEn}Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.11,0:32:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的，他宣布背叛神\N{\rEn}It's true, he spoke against God
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.50,0:32:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向奉行官井上大人\N{\rEn}to the Inquisitor Inoue Sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.50,0:32:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但那是八年前了\N{\rEn}- But that was eight years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.81,0:32:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他全家都被检验\N{\rEn}- His whole family was put to test.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.28,0:32:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说背叛神\N{\rEn}He spoke against God.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.34,0:32:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他仍相信\N{\rEn}But he still believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.01,0:32:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不\N{\rEn}- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.21,0:32:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们需要传教士在五岛。不，不，神父\N{\rEn}- They need priests on Goto. - No, no Padre.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.26,0:32:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是茂吉，我们会回到这儿\N{\rEn}But Mokichi we will return here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.50,0:32:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不，不，神父！- 我们会回到这儿\N{\rEn}- No, no, Padre! - We will return here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.84,0:32:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不认识五岛的人\N{\rEn}I do not know the people of Goto,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.14,0:32:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此我不知他们是否可信\N{\rEn}So I do not know they can be trusted.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.07,0:32:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们是基督徒，跟我们一样\N{\rEn}These are Christians. Like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.60,0:32:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉次郎叫他们来这里，我不知何故\N{\rEn}Kichijiro told them to come here. I am not sure why.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.90,0:33:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他为何做这一切？- 吉次郎带我们来到友義村这儿\N{\rEn}- Why does he do anything? - Kichijiro brought us here to Tomogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.88,0:33:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只是待几天\N{\rEn}It will only be for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.23,0:33:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，一人留在这儿？拜托\N{\rEn}But one will stay here? Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.50,0:34:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正丢下他们\N{\rEn}We're losing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.00,0:35:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牧師大人\N{\rEn}神父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.00,0:35:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的，没关系\N{\rEn}だいじょうぶ，だいじょうぶやげ
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.50,0:35:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N{\rEn}はやく
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.00,0:35:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，是的\N{\rEn}そうだ，そうだ
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.13,0:35:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在旅途中感受到的恐惧逐渐消失\N{\rEn}The fear I felt on the journey faded away
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.88,0:35:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为迎接我的喜悦，几乎像我本人一样伟大\N{\rEn}Because the joy which greeted me was almost as great as my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.16,0:35:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使吉次郎看起来也是颇受欢迎\N{\rEn}Even the sight of Kichijiro was somehow welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.79,0:35:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感谢神把我带到这里\N{\rEn}I thanked God for bringing me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.85,0:36:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那天，信徒收到了新的希望\N{\rEn}On that day, the faithful received fresh hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.59,0:36:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我重获新生\N{\rEn}And I was renewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.39,0:36:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们则奔向我\N{\rEn}And they came to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.79,0:36:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只是五岛，还有基督徒不辞路遥\N{\rEn}Not only from Goto, for the Christians made their way
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.46,0:36:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翻山越岭，从别的村来\N{\rEn}through the mountains, from other villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.87,0:36:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉神本尊是如此之近\N{\rEn}I felt God himself was so near.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.40,0:36:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在此活得如此艰难\N{\rEn}Their lives here were so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.74,0:36:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们生如牲畜又死如牲畜\N{\rEn}They live like beasts and die like beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.00,0:36:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但基督不是为善良和美丽而死\N{\rEn}But Christ did not die for the good and beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.65,0:36:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那太容易\N{\rEn}That is easy enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.36,0:36:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难的是为悲惨和堕落而死\N{\rEn}The hard thing is to die for the miserable and corrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.23,0:36:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在这儿，我知道我是他们中的一员\N{\rEn}But here I knew I was one of them
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.77,0:36:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能分享到他们灵魂的饥渴\N{\rEn}and I shared the hunger of their spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.53,0:37:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又一个祷告得到回应，在五岛\N{\rEn}Another prayer was answered on Goto.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.70,0:37:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那儿我得到了首个真实消息\N{\rEn}It was there I learned the first real news
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.85,0:37:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某人可能知道神父费雷拉\N{\rEn}of someone who might know Father Ferreira.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.41,0:37:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父费雷拉\N{\rEn}Padre Ferreira?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.17,0:37:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，你认识他？- 是啊\N{\rEn}Yes, do you know him? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.79,0:37:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你见过他？- 是啊\N{\rEn}You've seen him? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.02,0:37:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何时\N{\rEn}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.19,0:37:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他给婴儿施了赞美\N{\rEn}He made a praise for infant.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.04,0:37:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 小孩。- 婴儿\N{\rEn}- Baby. - Infant.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.72,0:37:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有病人\N{\rEn}And sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.29,0:37:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在千町\N{\rEn}At Chimachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.71,0:37:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但，是在最严禁之前\N{\rEn}But was before that Problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.64,0:37:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如今何在\N{\rEn}Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.84,0:37:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠近长崎。长崎\N{\rEn}Near Nagasaki. Nagasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.64,0:37:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不晓得，我不晓得\N{\rEn}I don't know, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.01,0:38:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们渴望获得信仰的有形之物\N{\rEn}They are desperate for tangible signs of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.05,0:38:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我尽我所能\N{\rEn}So I provided what I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.53,0:38:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我担心他们看重这些简陋的信物\N{\rEn}I worry they value these poor signs of faith
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.85,0:38:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚于信仰本身\N{\rEn}more than faith itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.93,0:38:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们怎能拒绝他们\N{\rEn}But how could we deny them?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.63,0:38:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最终，我只得把念珠分掉\N{\rEn}And finally, I had to part with my rosary.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.65,0:38:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在五岛，我完全疲于应付\N{\rEn}In Goto, I was completely overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.57,0:38:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我施洗过上百的成人和儿童\N{\rEn}I baptized over a hundred adults and children.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.51,0:38:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聆听无数的忏悔\N{\rEn}Heard confessions without number.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.76,0:38:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有吉次郎的忏悔我觉得最有必要\N{\rEn}But it was from Kichijiro that I felt the greatest need.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.16,0:39:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没拿念珠。- 我不配\N{\rEn}You did not take the rosary. - I did not deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.12,0:39:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何\N{\rEn}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.04,0:39:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你背弃神\N{\rEn}Because you denied God?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.22,0:39:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\rEn}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.10,0:39:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了保命\N{\rEn}But only to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.99,0:39:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们全家，奉行官逼我们放弃信仰\N{\rEn}My whole family, the Inquisitor wanted us to give up our faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.13,0:39:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,踩踏基督像\N{\rEn}Stomp on Jesus,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.20,0:39:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我们的脚\N{\rEn}with our foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.21,0:39:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只需一下，即可活命\N{\rEn}Just once, just rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.76,0:39:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不愿\N{\rEn}But they would not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.08,0:39:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但... 我踩了\N{\rEn}But... I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.15,0:39:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我不会背弃他们\N{\rEn}But I could not abandon them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.63,0:40:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使我背弃了神\N{\rEn}Even if I had abandoned God.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.81,0:40:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，我看着他们死去\N{\rEn}So I watched them die.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.32,0:40:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论我去哪儿，我看到烈火、闻到焦臭\N{\rEn}Wherever I go, I see the fire and smell the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.12,0:40:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我看到你跟神父加佩...\N{\rEn}When I saw you and Padre Garupe...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.72,0:40:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...第一次\N{\rEn}...for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.48,0:40:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开始相信...\N{\rEn}I started to believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.00,0:40:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...神可能要我回去\N{\rEn}...that God might take me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.94,0:40:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为在我梦里...\N{\rEn}Because in my dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.50,0:40:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...烈火不再那么明亮\N{\rEn}...the fire was no longer so bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.64,0:41:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我听你的忏悔吗\N{\rEn}You want me to hear your confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.26,0:41:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赐福我，神父\N{\rEn}Bless me, Padre.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.28,0:41:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有罪啊\N{\rEn}For I have sinned.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.58,0:41:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在五岛的六天以及吉次郎的重拾信仰\N{\rEn}Those six days at Goto and Kichijiro's renewal of faith
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.23,0:41:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我觉得吾命甚有价值\N{\rEn}Made me feel that my life was of value
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.47,0:41:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我真的是对那些民众有用，在这个国家...\N{\rEn}And that I could really be of use to the people in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.10,0:41:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...地球的尽头\N{\rEn}...The ends of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.83,0:41:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奉行所来人了，他们在村里\N{\rEn}Men from the Inquisitor, they are in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.75,0:41:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们抓了市\N{\rEn}They took Ichizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.00,0:43:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们收到告发...\N{\rEn}We've been informed...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.50,0:43:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...你们中有人...\N{\rEn}...that some of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.00,0:43:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...比如这个可怜的人\N{\rEn}...like this poor wretch here...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.00,0:43:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...是基督徒\N{\rEn}...are Christians.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.00,0:43:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们年年上缴赋税...\N{\rEn}But we pay our taxes every year...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.50,0:43:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...为藩背徭负役\N{\rEn}...and do our duty to the State.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.80,0:43:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在庙里敬拜神祗\N{\rEn}We worship Buddha in the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.00,0:43:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚...\N{\rEn}I am well aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.50,0:43:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...你们都是良民\N{\rEn}...that you are all good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.00,0:43:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只要获悉...\N{\rEn}We only want to hear about...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.00,0:43:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...那些信奉着...\N{\rEn}...those who embrace...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.00,0:43:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...非法信仰的人...\N{\rEn}...the outlawed faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.30,0:43:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...和那些...\N{\rEn}...and those...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.00,0:43:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...窝藏他们的人...\N{\rEn}...who hide them...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.00,0:43:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迟早，我们将会知道他们是谁\N{\rEn}In time,we will know who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.20,0:44:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想告发的赏金\N{\rEn}Think of the price for information.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.50,0:44:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多的银币\N{\rEn}This much silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.50,0:44:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要显得极害怕\N{\rEn}Don't look so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.50,0:44:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们给他们三天时间\N{\rEn}Let's give them three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.30,0:44:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,松开他\N{\rEn}Untie him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.80,0:44:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有三天\N{\rEn}You have three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.80,0:44:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会放了这个人\N{\rEn}We will let this one go.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.50,0:44:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果三天内我们没收到任何消息\N{\rEn}But if we hear nothing in three days...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.20,0:44:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...除了他...\N{\rEn}...in addition to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.90,0:44:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...我还要带走三个人质\N{\rEn}...I will take three more hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.50,0:44:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四个人质都会送往长崎\N{\rEn}The four hostages will be sent to Nagasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.00,0:44:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有...\N{\rEn}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.00,0:44:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...他们中的一个...\N{\rEn}...one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.00,0:44:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...必有你\N{\rEn}...must be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.87,0:45:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 不，我们不怕死，神父\N{\rEn}- No, we are not afraid to die, Padres.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.18,0:45:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们永不背叛您\N{\rEn}And we will never surrender you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.39,0:45:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 没人该死。- 不，但是我们都危险\N{\rEn}- No one should die. - No, but we will be in danger
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.56,0:45:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论去留\N{\rEn}Whether you go or stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.68,0:45:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下，留下，我们永不背叛您\N{\rEn}Stay. Stay. We will never surrender you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.58,0:45:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他们会不断搜查，如果我们留下\N{\rEn}But they'll keep coming if we stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.98,0:45:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会摧毁全村，杀掉你们全部，若我们躲于此\N{\rEn}They could destroy the entire village and kill you all while we hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.18,0:45:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，我们别无选择，茂吉，只能如此\N{\rEn}Yes, we have no choice, Mokichi, it's the only thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.50,0:45:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样才会危险远离你们\N{\rEn}This would draw the danger away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.40,0:45:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以藏在吉次郎的岛上\N{\rEn}We can hide on Kichijiro's island.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.88,0:45:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的岛\N{\rEn}My island?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.26,0:45:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不会有差别，在那儿还是在这儿\N{\rEn}No, there is no difference between there and here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.86,0:46:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会去五岛，他们要搜查\N{\rEn}They will come to Goto, they will search.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.06,0:46:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样的事会发生在五岛\N{\rEn}Same thing will happen to Goto.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.82,0:46:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们应当离开\N{\rEn}They should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.41,0:46:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父应当离开\N{\rEn}The Padres should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.76,0:46:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样，我们将得救\N{\rEn}That way, we will be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.67,0:46:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能那样说\N{\rEn}You can't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.40,0:46:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们来传播上帝的教诲\N{\rEn}They came to spread Deusu's teachings!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.17,0:46:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能就这么抛弃他们...\N{\rEn}We can't just give them up...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.65,0:46:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...去遭受井上大人的酷刑，毕竟他们是为我们而为\N{\rEn}...to Inoue-sama's tortures after all they have done for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.39,0:46:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已把我们置于险境\N{\rEn}They've put us all in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.72,0:46:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不至于如此遭罪，神父没来的话\N{\rEn}We wouldn't be in such trouble had the Padres not come!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.85,0:46:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安静！安静\N{\rEn}Be quiet! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.27,0:46:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得保护...\N{\rEn}We will protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.56,0:46:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...神父\N{\rEn}...the Padres.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.03,0:46:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们得留下\N{\rEn}You will stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.89,0:46:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们必须挑两人加入我们\N{\rEn}Now we must pick two more to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.17,0:46:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我，茂吉和另两个人质\N{\rEn}Me, Mokichi and two more hostages.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.99,0:47:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁愿加入我跟茂吉...\N{\rEn}Who will join me and Mokichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.73,0:47:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...成为人质去荣耀上帝\N{\rEn}...and become a hostage to honor Deusu?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.52,0:47:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉次郎不是这儿的\N{\rEn}Kichijiro's not from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.17,0:47:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何不选他\N{\rEn}Why not him?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.12,0:47:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\rEn}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.44,0:47:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我们所有人着想，你愿去吗\N{\rEn}For all our sakes, would you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.37,0:47:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,官差不会太为难你\N{\rEn}The officials won't be so hard on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.71,0:47:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只抓友義村的人\N{\rEn}It's the people of Tomogi they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.35,0:47:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是这儿的\N{\rEn}He's not from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.35,0:47:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可能就是告发我们的人\N{\rEn}He could be the one who informed on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.58,0:48:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是告发者\N{\rEn}I'm not an informer!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.01,0:48:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父，告诉他们\N{\rEn}Padre, tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.86,0:48:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是告发者\N{\rEn}I'm not an informer!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.09,0:48:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告解过我全部的罪行\N{\rEn}I confessed all my sins!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.95,0:48:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那如果你收到了上帝的祝福...\N{\rEn}Then if you've received the Lord's blessing...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.00,0:48:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...实行之\N{\rEn}...act like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.20,0:48:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荣耀他，用你的命\N{\rEn}Honor Him with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.80,0:48:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得对\N{\rEn}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.70,0:48:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,荣耀？你说的是什么啊\N{\rEn}Honor? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.80,0:48:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真正的基督徒会懂\N{\rEn}A real Kirishitan would know!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.50,0:48:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要捣碎你的头\N{\rEn}I'm going to smash your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.81,0:48:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你\N{\rEn}Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.20,0:48:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,替我们去吧\N{\rEn}Go in our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.97,0:48:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你\N{\rEn}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.21,0:48:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父\N{\rEn}Padre.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.66,0:48:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是神父\N{\rEn}But Padre?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.10,0:49:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们被迫去踏踩圣像\N{\rEn}If we are forced to trample on the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.50,0:49:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想照做\N{\rEn}I want that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.92,0:49:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须祈祷以获勇气，茂吉\N{\rEn}You must pray for courage, Mokichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.22,0:49:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果我们不做他们要求的\N{\rEn}But if we do not do what they want,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.02,0:49:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本村的每个人都会有危险\N{\rEn}There can be danger for everyone in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.00,0:49:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会入狱\N{\rEn}They can put in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.27,0:49:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远出不来\N{\rEn}They can wait forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.77,0:49:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该咋办\N{\rEn}What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.00,0:49:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,踏踩\N{\rEn}Trample.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.50,0:49:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,踏踩\N{\rEn}Trample.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.20,0:49:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就踏踩吧\N{\rEn}It's alright to trample.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.26,0:49:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说啥？\N{\rEn}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.99,0:49:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能\N{\rEn}You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.38,0:49:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 茂吉，你不能\N{\rEn}- Mokichi. You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.70,0:50:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我做了这个给爷爷大人\N{\rEn}I made this for the Jiisama.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.94,0:50:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是我们的全部，直到你们来了\N{\rEn}It was all we had, until you came.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.40,0:50:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收下这个，请\N{\rEn}Take this, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.81,0:50:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以主之名\N{\rEn}In Jesus' name.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.94,0:50:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的信念给了我力量，茂吉\N{\rEn}Your faith gives me strength, Mokichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.76,0:50:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望，我能以同样多的给你\N{\rEn}I wish, I could give as much to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.11,0:50:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对神的爱很强烈\N{\rEn}My love for God is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.76,0:50:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那跟信念一样吗\N{\rEn}Could that be the same as faith?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.91,0:50:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\rEn}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.09,0:50:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，肯定是的\N{\rEn}Yes. It must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.50,0:51:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人是地球上最虔诚的神的生物\N{\rEn}These people are the most devoted of God's creatures on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.38,0:51:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父范礼安我告解，我开始怀疑\N{\rEn}Father Valignano I confess, I began to wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.87,0:51:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神予我们考验以测试我们，而他所做一切都是好的\N{\rEn}God sends us trials to test us and everything he does is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.76,0:51:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我祈祷能像主之子那样接受考验\N{\rEn}And I prayed to undergo trials like his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.08,0:51:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但为何一定要他们的考验如此可怕\N{\rEn}But why must their trial be so terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.90,0:51:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,且为何，当我看着自己的心\N{\rEn}And why, when I look in my own heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.65,0:51:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给他们的答复显得那么软弱吗\N{\rEn}Do the answers I give them seem so weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.40,0:52:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,踩(踏む)\N{\rEn}Fume.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.31,0:52:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都做了他们所命令的\N{\rEn}All of them did as they were commanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.01,0:52:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那还不够\N{\rEn}But it was not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.53,0:52:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我们极易被愚弄\N{\rEn}You think we're fooled so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.01,0:52:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有注意...\N{\rEn}We noticed...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.21,0:52:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...你的呼吸如何...\N{\rEn}...how your breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.09,0:53:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...马上变沉重\N{\rEn}...turned heavy just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.48,0:53:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能\N{\rEn}That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.28,0:53:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们是佛教徒\N{\rEn}Because we are Buddhists.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.49,0:53:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\rEn}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.24,0:53:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们试下另一个方式\N{\rEn}Let's try this another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.02,0:53:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吐这个...\N{\rEn}Spit on this...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.04,0:53:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...然后说...\N{\rEn}...and then say...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.03,0:53:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...你们所谓的圣洁的处女...\N{\rEn}...your so-called Blessed Blessed Virgin...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.24,0:53:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...是妓女\N{\rEn}...is a whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.40,0:53:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是基督徒\N{\rEn}You are a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.17,0:54:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是基督徒\N{\rEn}You are also a Christian.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:37.47,0:54:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老市不愿吐\N{\rEn}Old Ichizo would not do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.56,0:54:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茂吉没吐\N{\rEn}Mokichi could not.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.15,0:54:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有吉次郎吐了，余下没做\N{\rEn}But Kichijiro succeeded where the rest failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.26,0:54:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须相信他同遭痛苦，有如别人\N{\rEn}I must believe he suffered along with the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.62,0:54:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是基督徒\N{\rEn}You are a Christian, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.34,0:54:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们都是...\N{\rEn}They are all...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.50,0:54:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...基督徒\N{\rEn}...Christians.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.53,0:55:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带走他们\N{\rEn}Seize them!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.52,0:55:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们被给了米酒\N{\rEn}They were given Sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.21,0:55:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像罗马士兵把醋给垂死的基督\N{\rEn}As the Roman soldier offered vinegar to the dying Christ.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.00,0:55:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我祈祷，他们记得我们主的痛苦\N{\rEn}I prayed, they remembered our Lord's suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.30,0:55:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并获得勇气及安慰于此\N{\rEn}And took courage and comfort from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.55,0:56:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝(拉丁语)\N{\rEn}Deus.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.93,0:56:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝\N{\rEn}Deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.23,0:56:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天堂\N{\rEn}Paradiso.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.01,0:57:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上帝大人\N{\rEn}Deus-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.88,0:57:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请收下爷爷大人的灵魂\N{\rEn}Please receive Jiisama's spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.01,0:57:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷大人的苦难结束了\N{\rEn}Jiisama's suffering has ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.56,0:57:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收下他，主啊\N{\rEn}Receive him, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.08,0:57:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主啊\N{\rEn}Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.47,0:57:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主啊\N{\rEn}Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.53,0:57:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以您的荣耀\N{\rEn}In Your glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.26,0:57:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求您...耶稣啊\N{\rEn}Please... Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.45,0:58:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这使得茂吉四天才死\N{\rEn}It took Mokichi four days to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.65,0:58:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,临终，他唱了赞美诗。他的歌喉是那唯一的声音\N{\rEn}At the end he sang a hymn. His voice was the only sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.35,0:58:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,村民聚集在海滩上，始终沉默着\N{\rEn}The people of the village, who would gather on the beach, were always silent.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.99,1:00:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们被严密看守，所以遗体不能进行...\N{\rEn}The people were watched closly, so the bodies could not be given...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.67,1:00:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天主教的葬礼\N{\rEn}a Christian burial.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.25,1:00:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茂吉的遗体浸水太多使火焰燃起浓烟\N{\rEn}Mokichi's body was so heavy with water it turned the flames to smoke.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.42,1:00:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在最终烧着之前\N{\rEn}Before it finally caught fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.83,1:00:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烧剩的遗骨被抛入大海，这样他们就得不到祭拜\N{\rEn}Any bones that remained were scattered in the ocean, so they could not be venerated.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.54,1:01:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父范礼安，你会说他们的死不无意义\N{\rEn}Father Valignano, you will say that their death is not meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.95,1:01:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了，神听到了他们的祷告，当他们逝去之时\N{\rEn}Surely, God heard their prayers as they died.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.93,1:01:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他听到他们的痛嚎吗\N{\rEn}But did he hear their screams?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.17,1:01:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我该如何解释他的沉默，对这些人，已忍受如此之多者\N{\rEn}How can I explain his silence to these people, who have endured so much?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.78,1:01:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得竭尽全力去理解这些，亲自去\N{\rEn}I need all my strength to understand it myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.32,1:01:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可能是我最后一次向您汇报，神父\N{\rEn}This may be my last report to you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.34,1:01:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们得知差卒，上山搜寻我们\N{\rEn}Today we hear the guards, are in the mountains looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.09,1:01:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们决定：要安全需分开\N{\rEn}So we have decided it would be safer to separate.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.86,1:01:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 所以你才对？\N{\rEn}- So you were right?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.11,1:01:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 如果我们离开，他们还能活命\N{\rEn}- If we left, they might still be alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.02,1:01:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说那些，那不是真的！我们不用怀疑，留下会要我们的命\N{\rEn}Don't say that, that is not true! And we can not doubt. That will be our death.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.64,1:01:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们放弃了？就干这些？我们就会跑路？\N{\rEn}- Are we giving up? Is that what we're doing? Are we running away?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.20,1:01:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不！- 在他们已为我们而死之后？\N{\rEn}No! - After the people have died for us?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.94,1:01:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们不是为我们而亡！加佩，他们没有为我们而死\N{\rEn}They did not die for us! Garupe, they did not die for us!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.55,1:01:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我感觉象个懦夫\N{\rEn}- I feel like a coward.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.03,1:02:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的爱永远与你同在。- 我祈祷能坚强如你\N{\rEn}My love is always with you. - I pray to be as strong as you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.95,1:02:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父加佩将去平户继续使命\N{\rEn}Father Garupe will make for Hirado to continue the mission,\N{\rTop_cn}(注：平户，日本最古老天主教会所在地)
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.25,1:02:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我则重返五岛\N{\rEn}and I will return to Goto.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.25,1:02:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗西斯科！要活着\N{\rEn}Francisco! Stay alive.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.57,1:02:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要活着\N{\rEn}Stay alive!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.22,1:02:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父，我请求原谅我的软弱和怀疑\N{\rEn}Father, I ask forgiveness for my weakness and my doubt.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.00,1:02:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还恳请您记得\N{\rEn}And I ask you to remember
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.38,1:02:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父加佩跟我有您的慈悲有您的祷告\N{\rEn}Father Garupe and me in your mercies and in your prayers.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.33,1:02:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您忠诚的孩子\N{\rEn}Your obedient son.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.13,1:03:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想像着您的儿子\N{\rEn}I imagine your son.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.64,1:03:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钉到十字架上\N{\rEn}Nailed to the cross.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.00,1:03:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我嘴有如尝醋\N{\rEn}My mouth tastes like vinegar.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.98,1:03:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是五岛吗\N{\rEn}Is that Goto?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.21,1:03:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是五岛吗\N{\rEn}Is that Goto?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.96,1:03:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天父，赞您之名\N{\rEn}Father in Heaven praised be thy name.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.69,1:03:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是一个带来灾难的外国人\N{\rEn}I'm just a foreigner who brought disaster.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.36,1:03:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是他们现在所认为的我\N{\rEn}That's what they think of me now.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.60,1:04:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在梦到了圣·弗朗西斯·泽维尔\N{\rEn}I dream of now Saint Francis.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.14,1:04:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在这里找到的所有光荣的可能性发生了什么？\N{\rEn}What happened to all the glorious possibility he found here?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.41,1:05:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为基督做了什么\N{\rEn}What have I done for Christ?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.70,1:05:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为基督做着什么\N{\rEn}What am I doing for Christ?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.25,1:05:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为基督将做什么\N{\rEn}What will I do for Christ?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.12,1:05:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感到强烈的诱惑，我感到绝望的强烈诱惑\N{\rEn}I feel so tempted. I feel so tempted to despair.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.02,1:05:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕\N{\rEn}I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.99,1:05:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等待的你的沉默是可怕的\N{\rEn}The wait of your silence is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.73,1:05:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我祷告但我已迷失\N{\rEn}I pray but I'm lost.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.40,1:05:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫非我只是向虚无祷告？\N{\rEn}Or am I just praying to nothing?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.26,1:05:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虚无\N{\rEn}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.09,1:05:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为您不在那儿\N{\rEn}Because you're not there.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.29,1:06:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我祈祷您的宽恕\N{\rEn}I pray for your forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.37,1:06:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的报告突然结束\N{\rEn}If my report now comes to an abrupt end,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.70,1:06:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别以为我们死了\N{\rEn}do not think that we are dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.13,1:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为如果加佩和我死了，日本教会与我们同亡\N{\rEn}For if Garupe and I die, the Japanese Church dies with us.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.74,1:07:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我被跟踪了。你还好吗？神父\N{\rEn}I thought I was being followed. Are you alright, Padre?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.15,1:07:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\rEn}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.51,1:07:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父\N{\rEn}Padre?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.84,1:07:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何你要回到这儿？神父\N{\rEn}Why did you come back here, Padre?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.29,1:07:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方危险\N{\rEn}This place is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.50,1:07:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须小心\N{\rEn}We must be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.74,1:07:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悬赏叁佰个银币拿你\N{\rEn}There is a prize of 300 pieces of silver for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.60,1:07:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叁佰\N{\rEn}300.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.30,1:08:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犹大只得叁拾\N{\rEn}Judas got only 30.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.03,1:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有基督徒在别的村\N{\rEn}There are Christians in another villages...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.03,1:08:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不远\N{\rEn}Not far
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.15,1:08:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以藏那儿，我会照顾你\N{\rEn}We can hide there. I will take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.02,1:08:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去，请\N{\rEn}Take it. Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.24,1:08:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定很饿\N{\rEn}You must be so hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.07,1:08:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茂吉和我的家人很坚强，我太软弱\N{\rEn}Mokichi and my family stayed strong. I am so weak.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.44,1:08:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吗？你显然能照顾好你自己\N{\rEn}Are you? You can certainly look after yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.70,1:09:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要自私\N{\rEn}Not to be selfish.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.01,1:09:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你不一样\N{\rEn}I’m not like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.01,1:09:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已无处可去\N{\rEn}I have nowhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.11,1:09:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何处可容弱者\N{\rEn}Where is the place for a weak man?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.80,1:09:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,置身如此世道\N{\rEn}In a world like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.25,1:09:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想为茂吉和市告解吗\N{\rEn}You want to confess for Mokichi and Ichizo?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.50,1:09:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“你想做什么，快去做。”\N{\rEn}"What you will do, do quickly."\N{\rTop_cn}(注：《约翰福音》13:27)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.00,1:09:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您儿子对犹大所说的话，于最后的晚餐时\N{\rEn}Your son's words to Judas at the Last Supper.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.95,1:09:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他愤怒吗？当他说出它们\N{\rEn}Was he angry, when he said them?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.34,1:09:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是它们源自慈悲\N{\rEn}Or did they come from love?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.29,1:10:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？神父\N{\rEn}Are you alright, Padre?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.23,1:10:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你看上去很累。- 我没事\N{\rEn}- You seem so tired. - I'm alright.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.98,1:10:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我那鱼太咸\N{\rEn}That fish you gave me was so salty.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.50,1:10:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我口渴\N{\rEn}I'm thirsty!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.14,1:10:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么？- 口渴\N{\rEn}- What? - Thirst!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.43,1:10:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的主说过那话\N{\rEn}Our Lord said that.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.70,1:10:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我取些水。\N{\rEn}I get some water.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.50,1:10:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉次郎\N{\rEn}Kichijiro!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.54,1:10:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我取水\N{\rEn}I get water!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.55,1:10:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉次郎\N{\rEn}Kichijiro!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.32,1:10:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉次郎\N{\rEn}Kichijiro!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.91,1:10:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 抱歉，我掉了水，神父\N{\rEn}- Sorry, I dropped the water, Padre.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.50,1:10:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为有什么问题\N{\rEn}I thought something was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.26,1:10:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是别担心\N{\rEn}But never mind,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.80,1:10:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有条河在附近\N{\rEn}there is a stream nearby.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.04,1:10:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢喝多少就喝多少\N{\rEn}You can drink as much as you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.60,1:10:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这儿\N{\rEn}Here.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.51,1:12:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父！原谅我\N{\rEn}Padre! Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.88,1:12:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父\N{\rEn}Padre!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.86,1:12:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我祈祷神的宽恕\N{\rEn}I pray for God's forgiveness!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.79,1:12:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会宽恕吗？甚至是我\N{\rEn}Will he forgive? Even me?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.45,1:13:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神的保佑\N{\rEn}Blessed be God.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.97,1:13:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啥是...你名字是啥\N{\rEn}What is...what is your name?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.31,1:13:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫尼加\N{\rEn}Monica.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.60,1:13:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，跟奥古斯丁母亲一样\N{\rEn}Ah, like the mother of Augustine?\N{\rTop_cn}(注：圣·奥古斯丁 天主教圣师，奥斯定会的发起人，公元354－430)
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.25,1:13:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的受洗名\N{\rEn}My Baptismal name.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.20,1:13:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这男子是约翰\N{\rEn}This man is Juan.\N{\rTop_cn}(注：Juan，西班牙语)
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.64,1:13:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他希望他的名字跟我们的传教士一样，约翰，逝者\N{\rEn}He wanted his name to be like our priest, Juan, who died.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.00,1:13:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在云仙\N{\rEn}At Unzen
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.31,1:13:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将会有更多的人步其后尘\N{\rEn}There will be many more joining him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.66,1:14:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你明白吗\N{\rEn}You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.39,1:14:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何你要那样看着我\N{\rEn}Why you are looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.32,1:14:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何你如此平静\N{\rEn}Why are you so calm?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.23,1:14:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们全都会死\N{\rEn}We are all about to die!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.65,1:14:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受酷刑\N{\rEn}Like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.58,1:14:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\rEn}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.84,1:14:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉，谢谢你\N{\rEn}I'm sorry. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.30,1:14:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的食物\N{\rEn}Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.27,1:14:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您\N{\rEn}ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.59,1:14:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是神父\N{\rEn}But Padre?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.09,1:14:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的神父\N{\rEn}Our Father,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.59,1:14:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父约翰...\N{\rEn}Padre Juan...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.50,1:14:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...说过如果我们死了...\N{\rEn}...said if we die...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:44.80,1:14:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...我们会上天堂\N{\rEn}...we will go to Paradiso?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.43,1:14:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天堂\N{\rEn}Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.03,1:14:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，是那样\N{\rEn}Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.09,1:14:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死了不好吗\N{\rEn}Isn't it good to die?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.80,1:14:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天堂是如此的好过此处\N{\rEn}Paradiso is so much better than here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.88,1:14:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人挨饿\N{\rEn}No one hungry.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.58,1:14:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从不生病\N{\rEn}Never sick.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.50,1:14:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有杂税\N{\rEn}No taxes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.58,1:14:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有重活\N{\rEn}No hard work.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.30,1:15:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，当然\N{\rEn}Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.05,1:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父约翰\N{\rEn}Padre Juan,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.25,1:15:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是对的\N{\rEn}was right
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.50,1:15:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...没有重活...\N{\rEn}...there is no hard work...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:10.50,1:15:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...在天堂里\N{\rEn}...in Paradiso.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.61,1:15:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本不工作\N{\rEn}No work at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.50,1:15:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有杂税\N{\rEn}There is no taxes.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.00,1:15:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有苦难\N{\rEn}There is no suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.60,1:15:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都将同神在一起\N{\rEn}We all will be united with God.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.83,1:15:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里不会有痛苦\N{\rEn}There will be no pain.
